title: A Dub for Chubb
description:
Mina Kimes and Domonique Foxworth talk some of the big trades on NFL Trade Deadline Day including Chase Claypool to the Bears, T.J. Hockenson to the rival Vikings & Bradley Chubb to the Dolphins. Plus, they recap MNF between the Bengals and Browns and talk about Jacoby Brissett’s surprising performance as QB1. They also give their Winners and Woofs for Week 8, show some love for Jimmy G, Christian McCaffrey, and the Eagles.
